162
00:16:42,172 --> 00:16:46,172
本日のライブのことをSNSに投稿する際は
When you post about this concert on social media...

163
00:16:46,172 --> 00:16:50,672
ハッシュタグ #holoIDChromaticFuture も
忘れずに付けてくださいわ！
Don't forget to use the hashtag #holoIDChromaticFuture!

164
00:16:50,672 --> 00:16:59,172
だってみんなのその…なんていうの、えっと…
情熱が！見たいから！
Because we really want to see your... how do you say... passion!

165
00:16:59,172 --> 00:17:02,672
そうっす！そうっすね！
Exactly! That's right!

166
00:17:02,672 --> 00:17:05,172
打ち間違えないでね！
Don't make typos, don't make typos!

167
00:17:05,172 --> 00:17:08,672
いえーい！絶対投稿してね！
Yay! Be sure to share it with everyone, okay?

168
00:17:08,672 --> 00:17:15,672
でも正直に言って
「インドネシアライブやるんだよ！」って 言われた時びっくりした？
But honestly, when you were told, "We're doing a concert in Indonesia!", were you surprised?

169
00:17:15,672 --> 00:17:18,172
もしもし？聞いてくれる？
Hello? Is anyone listening?

170
00:17:18,172 --> 00:17:21,172
そうっすね！
That's right!

171
00:17:21,172 --> 00:17:30,672
そうっす！あたしも同感！
妹のゼータに共感しているっす そうね、共感ね
Exactly! I agree too! I feel empathy for my younger sister Zeta. Yeah, empathy.

172
00:17:30,672 --> 00:17:31,672
カエラ・コヴァルスキアはどう？
How about you, Kaela Kovalskia?

173
00:17:31,672 --> 00:17:36,172
私もびっくりしたよ
なんかこう「え？マジで？」って感じ
I was surprised too, like "Huh? Seriously? For real?"

174
00:17:36,172 --> 00:17:43,172
なんかこう「え！ついにインドネシアで9人そろって ライブできるんだ！」って！マジかっこいいよね！
Like "Wow, can that really happen? Finally, and with all nine of us in Indonesia!" It's so cool.

175
00:17:43,172 --> 00:17:46,172
かっこいいっす！
It's so cool!

176
00:17:46,172 --> 00:17:51,172
はい、これが初めてホロライブ
インドネシアの9人全員でのライブだから
Yes, because this is the first live concert with all nine members of Hololive Indonesia.

177
00:17:51,672 --> 00:17:59,172
実はこれはホロライブインドネシアのファンに
とても重要な瞬間でもあるんだけど
Actually, this is a very important moment for Hololive Indonesia fans...

178
00:17:59,172 --> 00:18:03,172
世界中のみんなも見てくれるんでしょう？
But everyone around the world is watching too, right?

179
00:18:03,172 --> 00:18:05,172
いや、ちがう？
Or is that not the case?

180
00:18:05,172 --> 00:18:07,672
お答えして
Please answer.

181
00:18:07,672 --> 00:18:11,172
はいはい！みんなありがとう！
Yes yes! Thank you, everyone!

182
00:18:11,172 --> 00:18:16,172
でももちろんこれで終わりってわけじゃないよね？
But of course, our achievements won't just stop here, right?

183
00:18:16,172 --> 00:18:23,672
だから次はこう…世界征服ってのはどう？
我々はレディー！レディー！ レディーレディー！
So, maybe next we can... dominate the world? We are ready! Ready! Ready, ready!

184
00:18:24,172 --> 00:18:27,172
そうっよカエラ！ゼータ！
That's right, Kaela! Zeta!

185
00:18:27,172 --> 00:18:30,172
この機会におけるファンの支援に加えて
In addition to the support of our fans for this opportunity...

186
00:18:30,172 --> 00:18:35,672
このライブを実現させるために支援いただいた
スポンサーの皆様にも感謝申し上げまーす！
We would also like to thank all the sponsors who supported us in making this concert happen!

187
00:18:35,672 --> 00:18:40,672
ありがとうっす！ ありがとう！ありがとうっす！
みんなありがとうね！
Thank you! Thank you! Thank you! Thank you, everyone!

188
00:18:40,672 --> 00:18:43,672
サンキューサンキュー
Thank you, thank you!

189
00:18:43,672 --> 00:18:49,172
ところでこのライブって 何か違うところあるのかな？
カエラ気づいた？ 一番気が利くから
By the way, is there something different about this concert? Kaela, did you notice? Since you're the most observant.

190
00:18:49,172 --> 00:18:52,172
もちろんっす
Of course.

191
00:18:52,172 --> 00:18:56,672
もちろんそうだよ
こぼは気づかないと思うけど
Of course. I don't think Kobo would notice, though.

192
00:18:56,672 --> 00:18:59,172
これだよ
It's this.

193
00:18:59,172 --> 00:19:04,172
私たちの身体いつもとちょっと違うんだよ
Our bodies are a bit different than usual.

194
00:19:04,172 --> 00:19:06,672
かわいい！クルクル！
Cute! Spin, spin!

195
00:19:06,672 --> 00:19:12,672
かわいいかわいい！
Cute, cute!

196
00:19:12,672 --> 00:19:17,672
カメラこっち！こっち向けて！こっちこっち！
始まったなこれ
Camera here! Point it this way! Here, here! It has begun.

197
00:19:17,672 --> 00:19:21,172
ほらほら！こぼのかわいさを見て！
Look, look! See Kobo's cuteness!

198
00:19:21,172 --> 00:19:22,672
これこれ、お尻
Look, look, my butt.

199
00:19:22,672 --> 00:19:25,172
えー！お尻！
Eh, butt!

200
00:19:25,172 --> 00:19:31,172
おいおいおい こぼがカメラ全部乗っ取ってるじゃん
Hey hey hey, Kobo is hogging all the cameras.

201
00:19:31,172 --> 00:19:34,672
こっちにも向けてよ こぼだけには向けないで
Point it over here too, don't just focus on Kobo.

202
00:19:34,672 --> 00:19:39,172
いち、に、さん…はい終わり！こぼの番っす！
こっちにも向けてよ こぼだけには向けないで
One, two, three... okay, it's over! It's Kobo's turn!

203
00:19:39,172 --> 00:19:46,672
ストップストップ！やめてって！
カメラ全部乗っ取らないでよ！
Stop, stop, stop! Don't take over all the cameras!

204
00:19:46,672 --> 00:19:50,172
はいはい… それじゃあ
Okay, okay... Well then...

205
00:19:50,172 --> 00:19:57,172
やばいちょっと息切れた
ライブではしゃがない！ はいー
Gosh, I'm a bit out of breath. Don't fight in front of the concert stage! Okay.

206
00:19:57,172 --> 00:20:03,172
はいはいー はいよ
ゼータが怒ると怖いからね
Yes, yes. Zeta is scary when she gets angry.

207
00:20:03,816 --> 00:20:05,616
はいよ ゼータが怒ると怖いからね
Okay, because it's scary when Zeta gets angry.

208
00:20:05,616 --> 00:20:06,816
こわいよー
It's scary!

209
00:20:06,816 --> 00:20:13,116
もういいや ゼータがカメラを独り占めしちゃダメっていうのなら... うーん、しょうがない
Fine, if we're not allowed to hog the camera from Zeta... well, it can't be helped.

210
00:20:13,116 --> 00:20:15,516
ファンのみんなと遊ぼう！
Let's play with all the fans!

211
00:20:15,516 --> 00:20:20,216
さっきみんなからも大きな声をもらったわけだし 今度はこぼがみんなに大きな声を出したいっす！
Since everyone cheered loudly for us earlier, this time Kobo wants to make everyone cheer loudly!

212
00:20:20,216 --> 00:20:21,116
はいはいはい
Yes, yes, yes.

213
00:20:21,116 --> 00:20:25,216
そうっすよ、カエラの配信時間ほど長くはならないから安心して
That's right, don't worry, it won't be as long as Kaela's streams.

214
00:20:25,216 --> 00:20:28,816
そう！みんなにじゃなく、みんなとね
Right! Not at them, but with them!

215
00:20:28,816 --> 00:20:30,916
そうそう！そういうことっす！
Yes, yes! That's what I mean!

216
00:20:30,916 --> 00:20:35,716
だってこれから歌わなきゃいけないから まず声を温存しなきゃでしょ？
Since we have to sing after this, we should save our voices first, right?

217
00:20:35,716 --> 00:20:42,716
そうっよ、そんなにカエラの配信時間ほど長くはならないから安心して
That's right, don't worry, it won't be as long as Kaela's streams.

218
00:20:42,716 --> 00:20:46,816
まあいい 大声出していいから好きにして
Oh well, you can scream if you want, do whatever you like.

219
00:20:46,816 --> 00:20:49,716
みんな準備はいいかな？
Is everyone ready?

220
00:20:49,716 --> 00:20:52,816
いい感じ？
Feeling good?

221
00:20:52,816 --> 00:20:57,416
もう出来てるみたいっすね！じゃあこぼから！
Looks like you are! Then Kobo goes first!

222
00:20:57,416 --> 00:21:04,416
一緒に「BOKOBOKOBO！」って叫ぼう！よしいくよ！
Let's scream "BOKOBOKOBO!" together! Alright, here we go!

223
00:21:04,416 --> 00:21:08,816
いち、に、さん！
One, two, three!

224
00:21:08,816 --> 00:21:14,616
BOKOBOKOBO！
BOKOBOKOBO!

225
00:21:14,616 --> 00:21:17,416
いいわいいわね！次はゼータ！
Great, great! Next is Zeta!

226
00:21:17,416 --> 00:21:19,316
はいはいはい！
Yes, yes, yes!

227
00:21:19,316 --> 00:21:24,816
「ミッションスタート」って言ったら一緒に「スタート！」って言ってわ！
When I say "Mission Start", say "Start!" together with me!

228
00:21:24,816 --> 00:21:28,216
いいか？アアア！ミッション...
Ready? Ah, ah! Mission...

229
00:21:28,216 --> 00:21:32,716
スタート！
Start!

230
00:21:32,716 --> 00:21:36,216
次はカエラ！
Next is Kaela!

231
00:21:36,216 --> 00:21:38,816
よしよし！さてみんな そしてholol3roも
Alright! All of you, and holol3ro too...

232
00:21:38,816 --> 00:21:45,316
「holol3ro！」って言ったら「HU-HA！」で返してね！簡単でしょう？
When I say "holol3ro!", reply with "HU-HA!". Easy, right?

233
00:21:45,316 --> 00:21:48,616
さあさあさあさあ！
Come on, come on!

234
00:21:48,616 --> 00:21:51,116
準備はいい？ holol3ro！
Are you ready? holol3ro!

235
00:21:51,116 --> 00:21:56,216
HU-HA！
HU-HA!

236
00:21:56,216 --> 00:21:59,016
いいわいいわね！
Awesome, awesome!

237
00:21:59,016 --> 00:22:03,816
いいわついに３期生は息ぴったり
Great, the 3rd Gen is finally in perfect sync!

238
00:22:03,816 --> 00:22:07,716
そうわ まだまだ元気がありそうだね
Yeah, looks like everyone still has plenty of energy.

239
00:22:07,716 --> 00:22:11,516
だって、今日の一曲目だけ でももうすごく伝わってくるんだもん
I mean, we can already feel it so much from just the first song of today.

240
00:22:11,516 --> 00:22:16,216
みんなまさか私たちの１曲目が 「100%」だなんて思ってた？
Did you guys actually expect our first song to be "100%"?

241
00:22:16,216 --> 00:22:20,916
思うわけないよな 私もびっくりした
There's no way they expected it. I was surprised myself!

242
00:22:20,916 --> 00:22:24,816
ホシノヴァ気分でライブ開始だなんて！ すごいよね？
Starting the live in Hoshinova mode! Amazing, right?

243
00:22:24,816 --> 00:22:26,116
やばい！
Insane!

244
00:22:26,116 --> 00:22:30,916
かっこいいっすね、しかもさっきゼータとかが歌った... いや違う
That was so cool, especially when Zeta and the others sang... wait, no.

245
00:22:30,916 --> 00:22:32,016
ゼータとか？
Just Zeta?

246
00:22:32,016 --> 00:22:37,816
ゼータとカエラが歌った時は もう本家の「100%」みたいっす
When Zeta and Kaela sang, it was just like the original "100%".

247
00:22:37,816 --> 00:22:41,616
マジかっこよすぎるんだけど なんか、うーうー！ってなってき
It was seriously way too cool, it made me go "oo-oo!".

248
00:22:41,616 --> 00:22:44,616
あんなかっこいい歌を歌ったことあるのかな？
Have you ever sung such a cool song before?

249
00:22:44,616 --> 00:22:46,016
かっこつけてんの？
Are you trying to act cool?

250
00:22:46,016 --> 00:22:48,016
そう、かっこつけてる
Yeah, acting cool.

251
00:22:48,016 --> 00:22:51,216
本物のかっこつけ だってムーナの曲かっこいいもん
True coolness. I mean, Moona's songs are really cool.

252
00:22:51,216 --> 00:22:56,716
だってゼータがいつもスタイリッシュ とかジャズっぽい曲ばっかしょ？
Since Zeta usually only sings stylish or jazzy songs, right?

253
00:22:56,716 --> 00:23:01,716
だからさっき「100%」を歌った時 めっちゃ雰囲気か違う
So when we sang "100%" earlier, the vibe was totally different.

254
00:23:01,716 --> 00:23:03,816
しかもカエラのラップも！
And also Kaela's rap!

255
00:23:03,816 --> 00:23:06,816
なんかこう...
It was like...

256
00:23:06,816 --> 00:23:12,316
とにかくかっこよかった！すごくわ！
Anyway, it was super cool! Amazing!

257
00:23:12,316 --> 00:23:14,816
でも、それだけじゃないよ！
But that's not all!

258
00:23:14,816 --> 00:23:19,316
次の曲が「NEW zomBIE!!」でした！
The next song was "NEW zomBIE!!"!

259
00:23:19,316 --> 00:23:21,716
これだれの曲かわかるよね？
You know whose song this is, right?

260
00:23:21,716 --> 00:23:26,016
もちろんだよ うちの先輩だ
Of course we do, it's our Senpai's!

261
00:23:26,016 --> 00:23:31,816
holoroのパフォーマンスもめちゃかっこよかったよ まるでゲームの中にいるみたいだった
holoro's performance was also super cool, it felt like we were inside a game.

262
00:23:31,816 --> 00:23:35,716
そうっすわ！ しかもバックダンサーもいたし
That's right! And they even had back dancers.

263
00:23:35,716 --> 00:23:38,716
かっこよかったっすね！
It was so cool!

264
00:23:38,716 --> 00:23:43,716
他になんかあったかな？ レーザーも花火も！あと...
What else was there? Lasers, fireworks, and...

265
00:23:43,716 --> 00:23:47,916
すごいギミックがたくさんあったっすわ！
There were so many awesome stage gimmicks!

266
00:23:47,916 --> 00:23:51,116
あのバックダンサーたち あたしのソロライブに雇うっす
I'm going to hire those back dancers for my solo concert.

267
00:23:51,116 --> 00:23:53,916
おっと、もうソロライブの話？
Oh, talking about a solo concert already?

268
00:23:53,916 --> 00:23:56,816
まあ言葉も祈りってやつ
Well, words can be like prayers.

269
00:23:56,816 --> 00:24:02,816
でもこのライブはまだ終わらないよ！ まだまだ！
But this concert isn't over yet! Not yet!

270
00:24:02,816 --> 00:24:10,916
でも...さっき何の歌を歌ったか知ってる？
But... do you know what song we sang earlier?

271
00:24:10,916 --> 00:24:16,116
もちろんだよ 私の新しい曲だから
Of course, because it's my new song.

272
00:24:16,116 --> 00:24:19,316
そうっすね まあいいや
Right. Well, whatever.

273
00:24:19,316 --> 00:24:22,216
まあいい
Whatever.

274
00:24:22,216 --> 00:24:27,516
いやいや！タイトルは「dahlah.」だよ！ 「dahlah.」！
No, no! The title is "dahlah."! "dahlah."!

275
00:24:27,516 --> 00:24:31,916
おおなるほど
Oh, I see!

276
00:24:31,916 --> 00:24:36,216
「dahlah.」だったか... まあわざとだったけど 先に言ってよ！
Ah, it was "dahlah."... Well, I did that on purpose, but you should've said so earlier!

277
00:24:36,216 --> 00:24:41,816
だっていつもそれ言ってるじゃん 本当にまあいいやって思ってた
But you say that all the time, so I really thought you meant "whatever".

278
00:24:41,816 --> 00:24:44,616
それ言って帰ると思ってた
I thought you were just going to say that and go home.

279
00:24:44,616 --> 00:24:46,816
いやいや、かわいそうだから
No, that would be sad.

280
00:24:46,816 --> 00:24:48,816
じゃあ「dahlah」ってどういう意味？
So, what does "dahlah" mean?

281
00:24:48,816 --> 00:24:51,116
人生はしょうがないって意味
It means "life can't be helped".

282
00:24:51,116 --> 00:24:56,816
人生は重いからまあいいやって言えばいいだけ その後人生を続けようって意味
Life is heavy, so you just say "whatever", and it means "let's continue living life anyway".

283
00:24:56,816 --> 00:25:00,816
そうっね、大人になったらね
That's right, once you grow up.

284
00:25:00,887 --> 00:25:07,387
Untung lagunya santai, easy listening, jadi kita sambil keliling-keliling kan ya sapa fans kita, ya?
Thankfully, the song is relaxed and easy listening, so we can walk around and greet our fans, right?

285
00:25:07,387 --> 00:25:12,087
Asyik banget ya tadi ya? Aku juga suka banget tadi dance bagian reff-nya ya.
It was really fun, wasn't it? I also really liked the dance in the chorus.

286
00:25:12,087 --> 00:25:14,087
La-da-la-da-la-da...

287
00:25:14,087 --> 00:25:17,387
Itu... itu beda lagu gak sih?
Isn't... isn't that a different song?

288
00:25:17,387 --> 00:25:20,387
Gak gitu deh. Kayak gitu kah?
I don't think it's like that. Is it like that?

289
00:25:20,387 --> 00:25:26,687
Ya, tapi pokoknya asyik lah ya kalau nyanyi lagu chill, santai-santai kayak gini.
Yeah, but anyway, it's fun to sing a chill, relaxed song like this.

290
00:25:26,687 --> 00:25:29,687
Iya, santai dong.
Yeah, relaxed.

291
00:25:29,687 --> 00:25:33,687
Tapi ngomongin soal santai, kita tuh sebenarnya belum bisa santai dulu. Heh, santai.
But speaking of relaxing, we actually can't relax just yet. Hey, relax.

292
00:25:33,687 --> 00:25:37,387
Katanya gak boleh santai...
You said we can't relax...

293
00:25:37,387 --> 00:25:41,887
Iya, iya, jangan santai-santai! Jangan terlalu santai.
Yeah, yeah, don't relax! Don't be too relaxed.

294
00:25:41,887 --> 00:25:46,887
Karena konser-nya tuh masih panjang!
Because the concert is still long!

295
00:25:46,887 --> 00:25:50,887
Jadi sebelum itu, kalian ada nggak yang mau kalian sampaikan dulu?
So before that, is there anything you'd like to say first?

296
00:25:50,887 --> 00:25:54,387
Mulai dari ini nih, yang gak bisa diam.
Starting with this one, who can't keep still.

297
00:25:56,687 --> 00:25:57,887
Tiga kata saja...
Just three words...

298
00:25:57,887 --> 00:26:01,387
I love you.

299
00:26:01,387 --> 00:26:05,887
Keren, the best. Sangat jelas, ya.
Cool, the best. Very clear, yeah.

300
00:26:05,887 --> 00:26:13,887
Tetap semangat. Tetap semangat menjalani hidup, ya. Dah gitu aja. Pokoknya sampai akhir masih panjang, semangat!
Keep fighting. Keep fighting to live your life. That's all. Anyway, it's still a long way to the end, fight on!

301
00:26:13,887 --> 00:26:18,387
Saranghaeyo! Gomawoyo!
I love you! Thank you!

302
00:26:18,387 --> 00:26:21,887
Oke, kalau aku...
Okay, as for me...

303
00:26:21,887 --> 00:26:28,387
Ya... Semangat selalu! Semangat santai! Hidup jangan terlalu dibawa serius.
Yeah... Always fight! Relaxed spirit! Don't take life too seriously.

304
00:26:28,387 --> 00:26:31,887
Semangat santai ya? Semangat santai.
Relaxed spirit, huh? Relaxed spirit.

305
00:26:31,887 --> 00:26:35,887
Oke, kalau gitu kita lanjutkan!
Okay, in that case, let's continue!

306
00:26:35,887 --> 00:26:41,887
Weits, weits, tunggu dulu. Sebelum selesai-selesai ini nih ya...
Whoa, whoa, wait a minute. Before we finish all of this...

307
00:26:41,887 --> 00:26:45,887
Kita teriak bareng-bareng penonton dulu gak sih?
Why don't we scream together with the audience first?

308
00:26:45,887 --> 00:26:49,387
Iya dong! Ayo! Ayo!
Of course! Let's do it! Let's go!

309
00:26:49,387 --> 00:26:52,387
Oke, oke. Jadi...
Okay, okay. So...

310
00:26:52,387 --> 00:26:57,887
Kita teriak bareng ya? Dalam hitungan ketiga, kita sama-sama teriak 'Chromatic Future'. Oke, ya?
We'll scream together, okay? On the count of three, let's all scream 'Chromatic Future'. Okay?

